OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy across the north with
OL,6,Fsome heavy shower for northern England
OL,7,Flater. Elsewhere, sunny spells with
OL,8,Ffurther showers developing, heaviest
OL,9,Facross Wales, the Midlands, southern
OL,10,Fand eastern England. Slightly warmer
OL,11,Ffor most but cooler across the
OL,12,Fnorthwest.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FEvening showers fade leaving
OL,15,Fclear spells. Some rain may persist in
OL,16,Ffar northern England. Local frost in
OL,17,Fthe northwest, with rural grass frost
OL,18,Fand isolated fog patches south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
