OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FBand of rain moves south
OL,6,Facross Scotland, Northern Ireland and
OL,7,Fnorthern England. Scattered heavy
OL,8,Fshowers in Wales and the Midlands.
OL,9,FBrighter further north. Warm in the
OL,10,Fsouth, colder further north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
